## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-141">如果调用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> , 并且没有任何要向后定位到的文档, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>则不会执行导航, 并引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-141">If you call <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> and there are not any documents to navigate back to, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> does not perform a navigation and an exception is thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-142">如果需要, 可以检查<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>属性的值, 以确定是否存在要向后定位到的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-142">If you need to, you can inspect the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> property to determine whether there are documents to navigate back to.</span></span>  
  
   
  
