## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>在实现它的文档加载完成之前, 不应调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-161">可以通过处理<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件来检测文档的加载完成时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-162">下面的示例演示如何使用[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>从应用程序调用文档中的脚本函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-163">在此示例中, 脚本函数没有参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-164">下面是[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]实现将从[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]调用的脚本函数的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-165">下面演示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]了用于调用[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档中的脚本函数的实现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>在实现它的文档加载完成之前, 不应调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-174">可以通过处理<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件来检测文档的加载完成时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-175">如果未将足够的参数值传递给要调用的脚本, 则未将值传递给的参数将具有未定义的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-176">如果传递的参数值过多, 将忽略多余的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-177">下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>从应用程序调用文档中的脚本函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-178">在此示例中, 脚本函数需要参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-179">下面是实现将从[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]调用的脚本函数的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-180">下面演示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]了用于调用[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档中的脚本函数的实现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-194">调用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 与<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>设置属性的效果相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>需要以声明方式指定初始化时<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>导航到的初始文档的开发人员使用标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-196"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29>使用方法导航到可能包含转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-197">使用方法导航<xref:System.Uri>到不包含转义符的。 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6bd8-198">下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>通过<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>方法导航到文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6bd8-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
